## ðŸ“¦ API Endpoints

### GET /api/products
Get all products (supports `category`, `page`, `limit` query params)

### GET /api/products/:id
Get a product by ID

### POST /api/products
Create a product (requires `x-api-key` header)

### PUT /api/products/:id
Update a product (requires `x-api-key` header)

### DELETE /api/products/:id
Delete a product (requires `x-api-key` header)

### GET /api/products/search/q?q=term
Search products by name

### GET /api/products/stats/summary
Get product count by category

